snippet.title: Louie's Mansion - Trailer
snippet.description:
Louie's back at it again bois!

Louie gets invited to a mansion full of food, but soon finds out
the only food there is ghost and dust! Louie, along with the brilliant 
and amazing President set out to repay their debt and save Olimar!
Will Louie make it out alive? Probably... I mean he is Louie after all
(But will they repay the debt and save Olimar OOOoooooOOOooh!!!!)
(Also this trailer made it into the Nintendo Fan Game Direct, yeah wahoo)

This project is in the works and will hope come out soon, probably early 2024
